{{Effect at cast time end}}
* The recoil can be used to pass through terrain. 
* If '''Caitlyn''' buffers {{ai|Piltover Peacemaker|Caitlyn}} during ''90 Caliber Net's'' cast time, {{ai|Piltover Peacemaker|Caitlyn}} will start after the cast time.
** If '''Caitlyn''' buffers an ability or [[basic attack]] during this ability's cast time, the buffered ability or basic attack will instead start after the dash ends.
** Other abilities can be cast while {{tip|dash|dashing}} if they are input after the cast time.
* ''90 Caliber Net's'' missile will fail to fire if '''Caitlyn''' is {{tip|suppression|suppressed}} during the cast time.{{bug|2}}
